Norilsk Nickel Climbs on Billionaire Usmanov Plan to Buy

-- B y   J a s o n   C o r c o r a n
-- 
2011-03-14T16:05:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/norilsk-nickel-climbs-on-billionaire-usmanov-plan-to-buy-1-.html
OAO GMK Norilsk Nickel advanced for
the first time in four days after billionaire Alisher Usmanov
said his OAO Metalloinvest holding company plans to buy shares
in  Russia ’s largest mining company.  The stock added 2.1 percent to 6,913 rubles by the 6:45
p.m. close in Moscow, its biggest gain in two weeks.  “The board of Metalloinvest recently approved a plan to
buy Norilsk shares,” Usmanov said in a telephone interview.
“The 4 percent of Norilsk that I have now will be transferred
to Metalloinvest during the year.”  To contact the reporter on this story:
